en_565138_0	Paddy Marketing Board commenced purchasing of paddy of Yala Season from the Ampara District.
en_565138_1	Purchasing of a kilogram of Nadu Paddy for 38 rupees and a kilogram of Samba Paddy for 41 rupees was commenced at Uhana Weranketagoda Paddy Storage Complex.
en_565138_2	The Paddy Marketing Board has made arrangements to purchase paddy from the time of harvesting to avoid the congestion when purchasing paddy.
en_565138_3	The government has allocated 975 million rupees to purchase 25 metric tons of paddy from the Ampara District.
